| Excavated_items = Fragments of mirrors, iron swords, and arrowheads<br />{{ill|Miyama-style special pedestal and jar|ja|特殊器台・特殊壺}}<br />{{ill|Cylindrical haniwa|ja|円筒埴輪}}
